name: avontuur // 1
description:
avontuur is a dutch word that means adventure.

every adventure to a new place, we will be presented at every turn that we pass will provide surprises and something you have never seen and imagined before. 

in this avontuur series, i will submit photos of moments when i am on an adventure trip to a new place i have never visited. may seem simple, but i enjoy every surprise given from the moment of the journey of the adventure.

avontuur // 1 taken while on a motorbike trip in the middle of the night in bali, indonesia.
